However, I have an intuition recently.

190
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,000
It's very strong.

191
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,400
What is it?

192
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,760
I've found some clues at home.

193
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:56,040
I think that Ye Sirong

194
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,200
is not the murderer of my father.

195
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,240
