in everything.

210
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:30,840
He must have visited this place
and planned the route in advance.

211
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:32,200
That's why he could perfectly evade

212
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:34,160
the frontal areas
covered by the CCTV cameras.

213
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:35,800
But it is a large area.

214
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,760
