to completely conceal himself.

215
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,600
He must have left some traces.

216
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,120
How about this?

217
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:43,160
I will check all video footage again

218
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,600
to look for clues.

219
