I believe in you.

292
00:19:55,280 --> 00:19:57,400
You have the courage to face everything.

293
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,200
A nice girl like you

294
00:19:59,600 --> 00:20:01,360
deserves a better life.

295
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:04,200
Thank you, Aunt Lin.

296
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:06,640
However,

297
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:10,840
I don't ask for much now.

298
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,120
I have planned everything.

299
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:15,000
Once I got a job

300
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:17,200
and settled down,

301
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:20,080
I will take my mom

302
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:22,800
to leave the Zhou family,

303
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,840
and leave A Yan.

304
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,160
What are you saying, Xiaomeng?

305
00:20:28,320 --> 00:20:29,560
You said you'd leave A Yan?

306
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:30,640
No, you...

307
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:33,320
I...

308
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,320
I admit it's selfish of me to say this,

309
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:36,640
but I...

310
