I think if one day you really leave A Yan,

311
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:43,200
he might turn into a very terrible person.

312
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:45,880
But do you know that

313
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:48,040
if I don't leave him,

314
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:50,560
I fear that my life

315
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,560
would be even more terrible.

316
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,720
How about this?

317
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:55,800
Give me a chance. I'll help you.

318
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,280
