don't want help from anyone.

324
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:12,320
Didn't you say you believe in me?

325
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,600
You just need to wish me good luck.

326
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,880
All right then.

327
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:23,120
I respect your decision.

328
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:25,800
But please listen to me, Xiaomeng.

329
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:27,640
You have to promise me that

330
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:31,240
whenever and wherever

331
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:33,240
