332
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:36,520
I'll be the first person you call, okay?

333
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,640
Sure.

334
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:42,400
I'll remember that, Aunt Lin.

335
00:21:44,360 --> 00:21:45,480
I'm so sorry

336
