that you have to suffer.

337
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:50,080
I'm sorry.

338
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:55,680
I'm leaving now.

339
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:01,320
Aunt,

340
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:03,320
