341
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:04,600
I'll visit you again.

342
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,240
You're leaving?

343
00:22:09,040 --> 00:22:10,600
You have to come more often.

344
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:12,640
I am alone here. I'm bored.

345
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:14,800
Are you leaving now?

346
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,200
I will see you out.

347
00:22:16,280 --> 00:22:17,440
Please don't trouble yourself, Aunt.

348
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,560
Chairman Zhou, I'll see myself out.

349
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:21,880
Take care of Aunt.

350
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:23,840
Guang is not here. I'll give you a ride.

351
00:22:24,040 --> 00:22:25,800
Chairman Zhou, it's really not necessary.

352
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:27,960
I'll take a taxi. It's fine.

353
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,040
A Yan,

354
00:22:29,120 --> 00:22:32,040
