357
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:39,640
I shall oblige then.

358
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,440
Thank you, Auntie.

359
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:43,400
You're welcome.

360
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,440
Miss Sun,

361
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,840
