362
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,560
I will come more often.

363
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,280
Bye-bye.

364
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,520
I'd like to get off for some fresh air.

365
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:28,640
May I?

366
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,680
It's a nice view.

367
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,480
What do you think, Chairman Zhou?

368
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:02,360
Yes, it is.

369
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:10,480
Actually, I'm feeling a bit dreamy
right now.

370
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:13,720
I feel like I am enjoying the night view
with my boyfriend here.

371
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:17,680
A Yan,

372
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,440
I...

373
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,440
