what you're talking about.

378
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:54,160
Since I first met you at the pub.

379
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:57,360
Since I met you at my interview
at Shenghai.

380
00:24:58,600 --> 00:25:00,000
Since we worked overtime together.

381
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:01,720
Since you took me
to the celebration party.

382
00:25:02,360 --> 00:25:03,560
Since we had a business trip together.

383
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,720
I don't know since when

384
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:09,240
you have slowly become

385
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:12,000
the most important person in my heart.

386
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:16,080
You are serious. You are smart.

387
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:18,240
You are focused. Everything about you,

388
00:25:19,120 --> 00:25:20,800
has enchanted me and impressed me.

389
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:24,720
Chairman Zhou, I...

390
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:31,680
I'm sorry.

391
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:36,880
If you don't like me,

392
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:38,680
why have you never rejected me?

393
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:40,760
That's why I've said I'm sorry.

394
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:43,640
I have never thought about being with you.

395
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:46,360
I don't know why you have misunderstood.

396
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,360
Why don't you give me a chance?

397
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:54,240
You have someone you love already.

398
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:55,720
Am I right?

399
00:25:57,720 --> 00:25:59,000
That is private.

400
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:06,680
I see.

401
00:26:08,520 --> 00:26:10,200
It's me who should apologize.

402
00:26:10,520 --> 00:26:11,760
I've misunderstood.

403
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,160
I've thought too much.

404
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:15,360
I've put our relationship
in an awkward situation.

405
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:18,880
I hope you could find someone
that deserves you.

406
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,960
This is not comforting at all.

407
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,680
On the contrary,
it makes me feel even worse.

408
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:28,760
Chairman Zhou,

409
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,280
I guess you have never consoled

410
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,640
anyone that has been hurt by you.

411
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:49,840
(Investment and Partnership Party
for Dikai Commercial City)

412
00:26:58,600 --> 00:26:59,560
Dad,

413
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,880
does our presence
at these pretentious banquets

414
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,440
have any positive effect?

415
00:27:04,040 --> 00:27:05,120
Of course.

416
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:07,920
Today, we came for

417
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,200
the Dikai Commercial City Project.

418
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:13,840
The owners of some big brands
will be here.

419
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:16,000
They will be the targeted
business partners

420
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:18,280
of our Commercial City.

421
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:21,280
If they open their shops in Dikai,

422
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:24,680
other brands will follow suit.

423
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,720
If there are female CEOs,

424
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,520
do I need to flirt with them?

425
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:30,960
Be serious.

426
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:34,520
You have to put on a good show tonight.

427
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:36,920
President Jiang.

428
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:38,360
President Zhang.

429
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:51,760
The Farmer's Spring

430
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:53,720
