with Miss Zitong.

431
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:56,160
(Nongfu Spring)

432
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:57,800
Thank you, Director Liu.

433
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:03,960
I wonder if Miss Zitong is interested
in our brand, Boloni?

434
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,600
Boloni, I've heard of it.

435
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:08,040
I like your products very much.

436
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,360
Thank you.

437
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:11,760
Miss Zitong is so young and pretty.

438
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:12,800
Yes.

439
00:28:16,280 --> 00:28:18,120
Excuse me. I have a friend over there.

440
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,040
I'll be back in a minute.

441
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,000
Sure. Please.

442
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:24,840
Do you remember me?

443
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:26,960
Sure, you're Zitong,

444
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:28,280
Xiaomeng's friend.

445
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:30,080
I didn't expect to see you here.

446
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:32,600
They want me to endorse their brand,

447
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:33,920
so they've invited me.

448
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:34,800
How about you?

449
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,560
I am in charge
of a Commercial City Project.

450
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,440
We are currently inviting brands
to join us,

451
00:28:40,120 --> 00:28:41,000
so...

452
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,320
my dad forced me to come and socialize.

453
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:47,760
Actually, I don't enjoy
these occasions either.

454
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,280
I don't know what to say.

455
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:51,400
And those bosses

456
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:53,280
keep staring at me.

457
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:56,960
It is a compliment that they stare at you.

458
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:01,200
How about you? Won't you compliment me?

459
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,800
You already have so many compliments.

460
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:04,240
You don't need mine.

461
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:07,800
A Ze!

462
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:10,720
A Ze, come here.

463
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,440
The kids nowadays...

464
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:21,200
It's all right.

465
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,440
I'm getting out of here.

466
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:24,960
The air outside is much fresher than here.

467
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:27,240
Sure. I will accompany you.

468
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:33,760
You are Xiaomeng's classmate.

469
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:35,680
Are you around the same age with her?

470
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:38,360
Yes, we are the same age.

471
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:41,440
You seem to have a more mature look.

472
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:46,560
Do you mean that I look older?

473
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,800
Of course not.

474
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,360
Being mature is a merit.

475
00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:51,800
You and Xiaomeng have different styles

476
00:29:52,280 --> 00:29:53,080
and different strengths.

477
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:56,280
Actually, this is not my usual self.

478
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,040
I am here to socialize today.

479
00:29:58,560 --> 00:30:00,080
All right. I'm praising you.

480
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,280
Don't think too much.

481
00:30:01,840 --> 00:30:02,640
Right.

482
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:04,400
Have you met Xiaomeng recently?

483
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:06,600
Yes, of course.

484
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:08,080
We are best friends.

485
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,960
Yes, I know.

486
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:11,960
How is Xiaomeng lately?

487
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,480
The last time I met her,

488
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:16,160
she was worried about job hunting.

489
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,400
She...

490
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:21,160
Those previous incidents
have a great impact on her.

491
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:23,800
So it's not easy for her to find jobs.

492
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:26,680
This is my fault.

493
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:28,760
I didn't expect those photos

494
00:30:29,360 --> 00:30:30,720
would bring such a negative impact on her.

495
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:33,800
Well, are you and Xiaomeng

496
00:30:34,320 --> 00:30:35,880
in a romantic relationship?

497
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,640
Of course not.

498
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,400
I like her very much,

499
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:42,840
but she has never accepted my love.

500
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:49,480
Actually, Xiaomeng

501
00:30:50,320 --> 00:30:51,680
has someone in her heart.

502
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:53,880
Has she told you that?

503
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,120
She,

504
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,080
mentioned it in passing.

505
00:30:58,120 --> 00:31:00,200
Actually, an excellent man like you,

506
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:02,200
has no need to confine yourself
to Xiaomeng alone.

507
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:05,080
My point is,

508
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:07,480
a rich and handsome bachelor like you

509
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,600
can have better options

510
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:10,440
if you want.

511
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:16,200
Actually, I have had many girlfriends,

512
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:19,160
when I was young and all about fun.

513
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,360
But since I've met Xiaomeng,

514
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:23,360
I only want to be with her.

515
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:27,200
Although she looks weak on the outside,

516
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,240
she has a very strong mind.

517
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:31,480
Sometimes, she even has a little temper.

518
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:36,080
I can't really tell how she attracts me.

519
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:38,440
But every time when I see her,

520
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,000
I just feel very happy.

521
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,640
Actually, I understand your feelings
very well.

522
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,280
Xiaomeng is a lucky girl

523
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:51,040
to have you protecting and caring for her.

524
00:31:52,120 --> 00:31:53,160
I hope Xiaomeng

525
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:55,360
would treasure your love.

526
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:57,840
Thank you.

527
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:01,880
I'm so jealous of Xiaomeng.

528
00:32:10,560 --> 00:32:11,440
Please excuse me.

529
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:14,200
I have to go back in
to greet those brand owners.

530
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:16,840
Will you return with me?

531
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:18,400
I think I'll pass.

532
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,720
I'm glad to see you today.

533
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:25,480
Shall we meet again some other time?

534
00:32:36,280 --> 00:32:37,320
Zhou Xiaomeng,

535
00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:40,080
I have to take everything from you.

536
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,240
