538
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,840
I think Miss Sun

539
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:57,520
is very pretty and very sweet.

540
00:32:59,840 --> 00:33:01,360
Does she like you?

541
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,560
It's late now. You should rest early.

542
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:06,160
I think she...

543
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:09,680
-Xiaomeng, you're back.
-Mom.

544
00:33:09,760 --> 00:33:11,080
Miss Sun was here just now.

545
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:12,480
A Yan gave her a ride back home.

546
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:13,760
I'm telling you,

547
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:15,720
Miss Sun is very fond of A Yan.

548
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,920
A Yan, do you like her?

549
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,320
You should rest now.

550
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,200
A Yan...

551
00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:32,040
Mom, it's late.

552
00:33:32,160 --> 00:33:33,560
Let's get back to our room and rest.

553
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:37,800
I mean it. Miss Sun is very pretty.

554
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,040
I like her, too.

555
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:54,560
Qiao Zhen.

556
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:56,040
I'm sorry, Xiaomeng.

557
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:58,520
It has been so busy in the station.

558
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:00,680
I could hardly take a break and sneak out.

559
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:01,840
How are you?

560
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:03,600
